gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Mavericks 109, Warriors 99
gameRecap.excerpt: The Mavericks defeated the Warriors, 109-99. Kyrie Irving led the Mavericks with 23 points, eight rebounds, and 10 assists as Luka Doncic added 21 points, nine assists, and three rebounds. Daniel Gafford continued his streak without missing a FG, as he went 5-5 tonight, reaching 33-33 over his last five games (since March 5th). Jonathan Kuminga led the Warriors with 27 points and four rebounds in the loss.
